Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.81,0:02:34.70,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H42009A&\c&HFFFFFF&}Ti si ljubazan i iskren, ali ekscentričan.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.85,0:02:37.73,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H1A5CD3&\c&HBCD3FF&}tsuyogaru suburi wo zenshin matotte tachiuchi
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.85,0:02:37.73,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H1A5CD3&\c&HFFFFFF&}Pravim se da sam snažna i takmičim se sa tobom.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.73,0:02:40.54,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&HBC9800&\c&HFFF4C5&}sunao na dake da to shigeki ga tsuyokute kurakura
Dialogue: 1,0:02:37.73,0:02:40.54,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&HBC9800&\c&HFFFFFF&}Samo od toga što sam iskrena osećam se ošamućeno.
