Dialogue: 1,0:21:55.02,0:21:59.80,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}banira soruto de... Burning Love...
Dialogue: 1,0:21:55.02,0:21:59.80,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Sa slanom vanilom... Vatrena ljubav...
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.10,0:22:12.48,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}amai dake nara soruto kakemashou
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.10,0:22:12.48,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Ako je samo slatka, sipajmo malo soli po njoj.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.83,0:22:22.69,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}dare yori mo motto motto watashi wo shitte hoshii kara sarakedashitai
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.83,0:22:22.69,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Želim o meni da znaš više, više od bilo koga, želim da ti otkrijem sve o sebi.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.69,0:22:26.10,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}demo dekinai no keiken nothing
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.69,0:22:26.10,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Ali ne mogu to da učinim, nemam nikakvog iskustva.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:26.10,0:22:27.88,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}modokashi sugiru
Dialogue: 1,0:22:26.10,0:22:27.88,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Tako je frustrirajuće!
Dialogue: 1,0:22:29.78,0:22:34.87,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HFFFADA&\3c&H6E6600&}demo amai dake no ai wa chotto
Dialogue: 1,0:22:29.78,0:22:34.87,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H6E6600&\c&HFFFFFF&}Ali ljubav koja je samo slatka...
Dialogue: 1,0:22:36.55,0:22:42.62,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}watashi ga motomete iru mono to wa chigau
Dialogue: 1,0:22:36.55,0:22:42.62,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}...se pomalo razlikuje od onoga za čime ja tragam.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.92,0:22:49.70,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}shiro to iwaretara kuro datte icchau
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.92,0:22:49.70,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Ako mi kažeš belo, ja odgovaram crno.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:49.70,0:22:55.30,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HF1FCE3&\3c&H486A1D&}sunao ni narenai amanojaku
Dialogue: 1,0:22:49.70,0:22:55.30,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H486A1D&\c&HFFFFFF&}Ne mogu da budem iskrena i uvek protivrečim sebi.
Dialogue: 1,0:22:56.56,0:23:03.38,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H806112&\c&HF6ECD9&}suki to iwaretara daikirai datte
Dialogue: 1,0:22:56.56,0:23:03.38,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H806112&\c&HFFFFFF&}Kada mi kažeš da me voliš, ja odgovaram da te mrzim!
Dialogue: 1,0:23:03.63,0:23:09.03,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&HF6DDDC&\3c&H602E11&}ureshii no ni nani itten darou
Dialogue: 1,0:23:03.63,0:23:09.03,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&H602E11&\c&HFFFFFF&}Iako sam srećna, zašto to govorim?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:09.62,0:23:21.46,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}amai banira ni soruto kakeru you ni
Dialogue: 1,0:23:09.62,0:23:21.46,Ending,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}To je kao sipati so na slatku vanilu.
